Dialogue: 0,00:11:03.240,00:11:04.240,辉英,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:04.240,00:11:11.740,辉英,,0,0,0,,So this is the black color here. This value is Ui, right? And the distance between Ui
Dialogue: 0,00:11:11.740,00:11:23.360,辉英,,0,0,0,,and this appropriate reconstruction is delta x over 2 times the slope. Right? So this value
Dialogue: 0,00:11:23.360,00:11:31.240,辉英,,0,0,0,,is Ui plus the slope times delta x over 2. Right? Yes?
Dialogue: 0,00:11:31.240,00:11:33.240,辉英,,0,0,0,,So for this V?
Dialogue: 0,00:11:33.240,00:11:34.240,辉英,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:34.240,00:11:40.040,辉英,,0,0,0,,So for this V function, like it's not all inclusive. Like should it just be R greater
Dialogue: 0,00:11:40.040,00:11:43.800,辉英,,0,0,0,,than 0 for smooth solution?
Dialogue: 0,00:11:43.800,00:11:51.120,辉英,,0,0,0,,So we have a proposal that should phi of R be greater than 0 for smooth solutions?
Dialogue: 0,00:11:51.120,00:11:58.240,辉英,,0,0,0,,Or sorry, phi of R equal to 1 for all R greater than 0? Is that what you are proposing?
Dialogue: 0,00:11:58.240,00:11:59.240,辉英,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,00:11:59.240,00:12:02.240,辉英,,0,0,0,,Okay. So we have a proposal that phi looks like that.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:02.240,00:12:03.240,辉英,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:03.240,00:12:14.560,辉英,,0,0,0,,So we have a proposal that phi has a function of R. So this is 0, this is 1. We have a proposal
Dialogue: 0,00:12:14.560,00:12:19.560,辉英,,0,0,0,,that is 0 here and 1 here.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:19.560,00:12:29.000,辉英,,0,0,0,,Okay. We'll take a look at if the proposal works. All right? Okay. So let's figure out
Dialogue: 0,00:12:29.000,00:12:30.680,辉英,,0,0,0,,the appropriate...
