Dialogue: 0,00:12:31.740,00:12:32.740,辉英,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:32.740,00:12:33.980,辉英,,0,0,0,,So we have the part of the proposal works. Yes?
Dialogue: 0,00:12:33.980,00:12:41.980,辉英,,0,0,0,,In the green figure, the cell to the left is it equal to Ui plus 1 as well?
Dialogue: 0,00:12:41.980,00:12:46.120,辉英,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry. The left should be Ui minus 1. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,00:12:46.120,00:12:47.640,辉英,,0,0,0,,So they don't have to be...
