Dialogue: 0,00:13:02.740,00:13:04.600,辉英,,0,0,0,,whenever r is less than zero.
Dialogue: 0,00:13:05.540,00:13:10.520,辉英,,0,0,0,,Does that give us the desired solution
Dialogue: 0,00:13:10.520,00:13:13.060,辉英,,0,0,0,,whenever we have a local extrema?
Dialogue: 0,00:13:15.540,00:13:16.860,辉英,,0,0,0,,Yes, right?
Dialogue: 0,00:13:17.260,00:13:18.980,辉英,,0,0,0,,Whenever we have a local extrema,
Dialogue: 0,00:13:19.140,00:13:22.480,辉英,,0,0,0,,we want a piecewise constant reconstruction
Dialogue: 0,00:13:22.480,00:13:28.220,辉英,,0,0,0,,because any slope is going to give us new extremas.
